  h2 Disk
  p There are two types of storage technology you should be aware of:
  ol
    li Magnetic aka "hard disk drives" (HDD)
    li Solid State Drives (SSD)

  p HDD is an older technology and is slower due to its moving physical components. However it is still used in many places and you may encounter it in cloud computing.
  p SSD is newer and faster storage technology, you would find such drives on phones and modern laptops.

